title: Warhammer 40k codex
description:
I uploaded this quite a while ago, and there are some codices that have since been updated.

Space Marines, Space Wolves, Imperial Guard and Tyranids are no longer current. There are many uploads available for each of these though, so with no effort you can get them.

I never did get a complete version of the 4E Space Marine codex, this is the same old incomplete one that we've seen for ages. Not that it matters anymore.
